  <div class="onepic intro-text introduction">
    <img class="banner-image">
	<h2 class="texttitle">Reproach</h2>
  </div>

	<div class="unopoem">
	<main>
	  <section class="poemtext">
		<div class="introduction">
		  <div class="intro-text">
			<p2>
      "Across an ocean of pain, we slump idle
      </br>
      Mouths empty where our own hunger eats us
      </br>
      Feces belittle our dreams of survival
      </br>
      Quiet we lay and wait till death greets us

      </br>Tears surmount the salt in the Atlantic
      </br>Prayers mean nothing to deaf Gods above
      </br>I recall, the weak among us vanished
      </br>The strong lived, but pain we are never free of

      </br>The land beyond was a hell of its own
      </br>Now split from our kin and owned by white skin
      </br>As I write, bondage is captured on phones
      </br>How much longer will we yield to their sin?

      </br>Teach us what it means to have peace of mind
      </br>Remind us what love is; patient and kind"
    </p2>
		  </div>
		</div>
	  </section>
	</main>
	</div>

